1
00:00:01,910 --> 00:00:03,770
No! I don't want to die!

2
00:00:03,770 --> 00:00:04,650
Shut up!

3
00:00:04,650 --> 00:00:08,810
Let go! This is why I 
didn't want to come here!

4
00:00:08,810 --> 00:00:09,740
Kimari-san...

5
00:00:09,740 --> 00:00:14,150
Shut up! If you want her to 
live, fork over the cash!

6
00:00:14,150 --> 00:00:18,580
Help me! I have a turtle 
and a hamster who need me!

7
00:00:14,710 --> 00:00:18,580
I'm sorry, I'm just a temp. You'll want 
to talk to the banking manager...

8
00:00:18,950 --> 00:00:21,080
This is no time to be playing around.

9
00:00:25,850 --> 00:00:27,330
You're still laughing?!

10
00:00:27,550 --> 00:00:31,590
She's right. It's not nice 
to keep laughing at her...

11
00:00:33,340 --> 00:00:37,260
Yuzuki-chan. That's the kind 
of thing that hurts most...

12
00:00:37,260 --> 00:00:38,600
Can you hear me?

13
00:00:38,950 --> 00:00:39,540
There it is!

14
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:40,640
Kimari!

15
00:00:41,400 --> 00:00:43,390
Rin! Mom!

16
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:46,160
What happened to your face?

17
00:00:46,160 --> 00:00:47,520
We've gotta take a picture!

18
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:49,900
That's the first thing you have 
to say after all this time?

19
00:00:50,510 --> 00:00:54,400
Sis, are you gonna do your New Year's 
Eve broadcast looking like that?

20
00:00:53,370 --> 00:00:54,400
My stomach hurts!

21
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,360
We're working on it...

22
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,860
Next. Miyake-san?

23
00:00:57,860 --> 00:00:58,410
Yes?

24
00:00:59,040 --> 00:01:03,300
Some friends of yours heard about this 
relay test and came to talk to you.

25
00:01:04,300 --> 00:01:05,490
Friends?

26
00:01:06,570 --> 00:01:07,420
Of mine?

27
00:01:07,870 --> 00:01:09,670
Miyake-san, it's been so long!

28
00:01:09,670 --> 00:01:12,670
We haven't heard from you for 
so long, so we were worried.

29
00:01:12,990 --> 00:01:14,550
What is it?

30
00:01:14,550 --> 00:01:15,570
Did it go down?

31
00:01:16,990 --> 00:01:18,030
Hinata?

32
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:19,980
Ouchies! My leg's cramped!

33
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:22,590
Shirase, sorry, you take over!

34
